<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>商品護照查詢｜SENWEI</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container nav">
        <a class="brand" href="/">
          <img src="/assets/logo.jpg" alt="SENWEI logo">
          <span class="brand-name">SENWEI</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="/" data-nav>首頁</a>
          <a href="/about" data-nav>關於我們</a>
          <a href="/product" data-nav>商品頁</a>
          <a href="/passport" data-nav>商品護照</a>
          <a href="/admin" data-nav>登入</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="container grid-2">
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow"><%= hero.eyebrow %></span>
            <h1><%- hero.title %></h1>
            <p><%= hero.description %></p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <img src="<%= hero.hero_image_path %>" alt="商品護照查詢示意圖">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container grid-2">
          <div class="form-card">
            <form id="passportQueryForm" class="form-grid" method="GET" action="/passport">
              <div class="form-row">
                <label for="batchNo">商品批次號</label>
                <input
                  id="batchNo"
                  name="batchNo"
                  type="text"
                  value="<%= batchNo || '' %>"
                  placeholder="例如：SNW-2026-001">
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">查詢商品護照</button>
            </form>
            <div
              id="passportResult"
              class="result-card <%= results && results.length ? 'show' : '' %>"
              aria-live="polite">
              <% if (results && results.length) { const r = results[0]; %>
                <div class="kv">
                  <strong>品牌</strong><span>SENWEI</span>
                  <strong>商品</strong><span><%= r.product_name %></span>
                  <strong>商品批次</strong><span><%= r.batch_no %></span>
                  <strong>護照代碼</strong><span><%= r.passport_code %></span>
                  <strong>護照摘要</strong><span>可追溯回收來源、公開檢測摘要與文件資訊（依後台資料）。</span>
                  <strong>查詢狀態</strong><span>已找到對應商品護照</span>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 16px;">
                  <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/passports/<%= r.passport_code %>?view=consumer">查看商品護照詳情</a>
                </div>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-card">
            <span class="eyebrow">查詢後可顯示</span>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size:2.2rem; margin-top: 16px;">前台可見的商品護照內容</h2>
            <div class="feature-list">
              <li>商品名稱與商品批次</li>
              <li>銀髮友善與環境友善摘要</li>
              <li>來源與檢測報告摘要</li>
              <li>未來可延伸的 QR Code / DPP 顯示入口</li>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <div>
          <div class="tagline">SENWEI</div>
          <small>銀髮友善護膚品牌｜環境友善保養理念</small>
        </div>
        <small>網站製作：來就補多媒體行銷</small>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

